issue.title: When user deletes hashtags the new ones should show up
issue.body: Meaning if a user chose to have 10 hashtags (assuming that is already implemented) or even the default 30, and then out of the ones generated he/she deletes say 5 that he/she didn't like, new 5 hashtags should show-up
